  "installSteps": [
    "<strong>Clone and build:</strong><br><code>git clone https://github.com/TMHSDigital/Plaid-Developer-Tools.git</code><br><code>cd Plaid-Developer-Tools/mcp-server && npm install && npm run build</code>",
    "<strong>Get Plaid credentials:</strong> Sign up at <a href=\"https://dashboard.plaid.com/signup\" target=\"_blank\">dashboard.plaid.com</a> and get your <code>client_id</code> and <code>secret</code> for the sandbox environment.",
    "<strong>Set environment variables:</strong><br><code>cp .env.example .env</code><br>Edit <code>.env</code> with your <code>PLAID_CLIENT_ID</code>, <code>PLAID_SECRET</code>, and <code>PLAID_ENV=sandbox</code>.",
    "<strong>Add to Cursor MCP config</strong> (<code>.cursor/mcp.json</code>):<br><code>{\"mcpServers\":{\"plaid\":{\"command\":\"node\",\"args\":[\"mcp-server/dist/index.js\"],\"env\":{\"PLAID_CLIENT_ID\":\"YOUR_CLIENT_ID\",\"PLAID_SECRET\":\"YOUR_SECRET\",\"PLAID_ENV\":\"sandbox\"}}}}</code>",
    "Open your fintech project in Cursor. All 17 skills, 7 rules, and 30 MCP tools are ready. Start with sandbox mode - switch <code>PLAID_ENV</code> to <code>development</code> or <code>production</code> when ready."
  ],
